reviewText: It's Christmas Eve, and Gullah Gullah Island is covered with...snow!  The yard is busy with elves. And look - here comes Mrs. Claus. Has Gullah Gullah Island turned into the North Pole or is Shaina just dreaming of a white Christmas?  Climb aboard the sleigh because we're off for a merry, music-filled holiday visit with the Alstons, Binyah-Binyah Polliwog, and all of their family and friends.
